Three comment types: single-line //, multi-line /* */, JavaDoc /** */. Single-line for brief notes. Multi-line for blocks. JavaDoc for API documentation. Good comments explain why not what. Keep updated with code. Don't over-comment obvious code. Example: // Calculate tax not // Add two numbers